title: Open Source Code
copy: We have open sourced a lot of our projects—big and small. Here are a few highlights:   View the central Data Aggregator on GitHub View our collection of data microservices on GitHub   View the iOS app code on GitHub View the Android app code on GitHub   View the JourneyMaker client on GitHub View the JourneyMaker CMS in GitHub   And much more We have a lot more open source code available, and we're planning on continuing to release more projects in the future.
